body: Fair enough. I liked this series because of its writing than the specific characters involved in it, and we got three other doujins out of this one anyway, so no big deal. Guess I'll just have to read your original stuff.
Oh and by the way I'm not finishing this. I'd rather focus on my new original series, "My Wife is a Pretty Cool Dude". I uploaded it to E-hentai, but won't copy it over to here tho (´ー｀)
I'd like Sayori a lot more if she'd been like this. I'd have liked DDLC a lot more, too. This version of her is great.
